theorem P2_of_P3_and_open_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) (hOpenCl : IsOpen (closure (A : Set X))) :
    Topology.P2 A := by
  -- First obtain `P1` from the given `P3` hypothesis and the openness of `closure A`.
  have hP1 : Topology.P1 A :=
    Topology.P1_of_P3_and_open_closure (A := A) hP3 hOpenCl
  -- Combine `P1` and `P3` to deduce `P2`.
  exact Topology.P2_of_P1_and_P3 (A := A) ⟨hP1, hP3⟩

theorem P1_of_P3_and_open_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) (hOpenCl : IsOpen (closure (A : Set X))) :
    Topology.P1 (closure A) := by
  exact Topology.P1_of_open_closure (A := A) hOpenCl
